# Monorepo Conventions

## Workspaces
Root `package.json` → `apps/*` + `packages/*`

## Package names
- `@venue-pos/api`, `@venue-pos/dashboard`, `@venue-pos/pos`, `@venue-pos/kds`, `@venue-pos/local-agent`
- `@venue-pos/shared`, `@venue-pos/i18n`

## Dependency rules
- Apps import `@venue-pos/shared` and `@venue-pos/i18n`
- Apps do **not** import each other (no `dashboard` → `api` code imports)
- Shared packages have **zero** app dependencies

## Root scripts (use these)
```bash
npm run dev:api|dashboard|pos|kds|agent
npm run migrate:dev    # Prisma dev migrations
npm run seed
```

## Adding a dependency
```bash
npm install zod -w @venue-pos/api
npm install react-router-dom -w @venue-pos/dashboard
```

## Ports (fixed)
| App | Port |
|-----|------|
| API | 3000 |
| Dashboard | 5173 |
| POS | 5174 |
| KDS | 5175 |
| Local agent | 3456 |
